Javascript arrays cannot have &quot;string indexes&quot;. A Javascript Array is exclusively numerically indexed. When you set a &quot;string index&quot;, you&#39;re setting a property of the object.

A.a = &#39;1&#39; and A[&#39;a&#39;] = &#39;1&#39; are equals.

